		 <span>&nbsp;</span> <a href="http://www.green-tourism.com/business/">Business Home</a> <span>&nbsp;</span> <a href="http://www.green-tourism.com/business/partners/">Partners</a> <span>&nbsp;</span> <a href="http://www.green-tourism.com/business/partners/destinations/">Destinations</a> <span>&nbsp;</span> Canada	</p>
